### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/api/healthz
Origin: http://localhost:5173

### CORS preflight
OPTIONS http://localhost:4000/api/handlers
Origin: http://localhost:5173
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET

### Handlers utan JWT → 401
GET http://localhost:4000/api/handlers

### Ogiltig JWT → 401 invalid_token
GET http://localhost:4000/api/handlers
Authorization: Bearer bad

### Rate-limit invites/accept (kör manuellt flera gånger) → 429
POST http://localhost:4000/api/invites/accept
Content-Type: application/json

{"token":"x","password":"p","name":"n"}
